        FROM [Dishes] AS [d]) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoriesId], [t].[Code], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[PictureId], [t].[Price], [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]

) AS [t]
